{"tid":408599,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《反斗小王子》20年拍真人日劇　19歲爆紅男模演邪留丸","createTime":"2017-09-21T10:59:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T05:01:05.000Z","uid":9573,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b59a140b64bcdc58a5cba2d18acc6ae345256b93","tid":408599,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T10:59:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/1859/e1859365.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1859%2Fe1859365.jpg&h=fc1e2566&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲《丸少爺》播出20年，電視台宣布拍真人日劇。<br />\n<br />\n日本人氣動畫《丸少爺》自1998年播出至今將滿20周年，故事中的5歲妖精小少爺「邪留丸」，曾長大成17歲的花美男，臉尖抽高的外型令觀眾印象深刻。該動畫為了慶祝播出滿20周年，宣布將於11月3日推出真人版電視劇，而且只有短短10分鐘！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/1859/d1859363.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1859%2Fd1859363.jpg&h=838af709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲5歲丸少爺動畫版曾變成17歲花美男。<br />\n<br />\n《丸少爺》描述平安時代的小少爺「邪留丸」，幾多重轉，循環中幾段情緣。 意外穿越到現代的月光鎮，住進小學生田村和真的家，偶爾和三個小鬼展開逗趣對決。該動畫2016年推出「17歲丸少爺」篇轟動一時，真人版沿用同樣設定，敘述17歲的丸少爺來到東京發生的故事，扮演男主角的是19歲模特兒後藤優太朗（ゆうたろう），消息一曝光馬上登上日本YAHOO話題熱搜冠軍。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2809/d2809041.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2809%2Fd2809041.jpg&h=abff1d17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲《丸少爺》開播20年，真人版描述長大的丸少爺來到東京。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2809/d2809201.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2809%2Fd2809201.jpg&h=f2e69c26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲《丸少爺》由男模後藤優太朗主演。<br />\n<br />\n後藤優太朗出身廣島，身高165公分，在原宿服裝店當店員帥到上電視爆紅，在眾人期待下出道當男模，開設推特突破18萬人追蹤。他的美形臉蛋深獲日本女性喜愛，每周末服裝店吸引各地粉絲排隊見本尊，現在要演出《丸少爺》，令動漫迷震驚不已，此外，其他主要角色由誰演出也令網友高度好奇。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2809/d2809047.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2809%2Fd2809047.jpg&h=6d901490&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲後藤優太朗在原宿服飾店當店員，人氣夯到出道當模特兒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/o_s3RwXa1CM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fo_s3RwXa1CM&d=FGuILpbWDgP7IrF7AAea7pUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=f8405955\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/o_s3RwXa1CM</a><br />\n▲《丸少爺》熱播20年萌翻各世代觀眾。"},{"pid":"8af2d4cca89ab5e5e76ba5e943538985a9218a79","tid":408599,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T11:00:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"805d44e6ba7e65dd56831d6d8ed39c1bacdd36fa","tid":408599,"uid":6116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T11:23:02.000Z","msg":"165 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f83e331678f174e919e59fb05c134d0f27f711","tid":408599,"uid":37757,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T11:24:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.nishikun.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/who-is-nishikun-728x380.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nishikun.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2Fwho-is-nishikun-728x380.jpg&h=1d28a221&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b89c2c018ce9164b72521492472847a2419908d","tid":408599,"uid":3794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T11:26:26.000Z","msg":"若巴係咪諗唔到插啲乜入嚟結果要插歌詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc37ffa63b2bba07c80d8507a05ebb87a35e6a2c","tid":408599,"uid":71073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T11:27:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://www.nishikun.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/who-is-nishikun-728x380.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nishikun.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2Fwho-is-nishikun-728x380.jpg&h=1d28a221&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n泰迪羅賓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b01ddf4ebc7002787e201974c133b4237d84db","tid":408599,"ui